DEI Analytics
The DEI Analytics app provides insights to improve DEI (diversity, equity, and inclusion) goals and employee relationships.
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions of Net Zero Cloud.
For more information on configuring the DEI Analytics app, see Enable DEI Insights in Net Zero Cloud.
For more information on DEI Analytics dashboards, see DEI Insights.
title: Improving Diversity and Inclusion with Salesforce Analytics
